  "title": "Merge clearAll and currentRefinedValues in a single widget",
  "body": "Those two widgets are really close.\n\nOne of them is a single \"clear all\" button, the other one is a list of the active filters plus a \"clear all\" button.\n\nWe need to review the API and use cases of those widgets to see if and how could we merge them.\n\nAs a user I would be a bit lost here, I would prefer to have a \"clearFilters\" widget that could do both with a straightforward API.\n",
